$ Visual Studio Code: Side Bar
@ Side Bar

The side bar is located either on the left side (but right of the Activity Bar) or on the right side. Its position can be moved with
→ development/editors/Visual-Studio-Code/GUI/menu/View/Appearance/Move-Side-Bar-Right_Left[View -> Appearance -> Move Side Bar Right|Left]

The → development/editors/Visual-Studio-Code#vscode-shortcuts[keyboard shortcut] `ctrl+0` moves *focus* to the Side Bar, `ctrl+b` shows or hides (toggles) the Side Bar.
